[Amit Varma]: Over 36 lectures, Dr. Fears will take you through life lessons contained in the works

00:02:47.780 --> 00:02:53.400
[Amit Varma]: of Seneca, Shakespeare, Plato, Aristophanes, Orwell, and my childhood favourite, Dostoyevsky.

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:57.520
[Amit Varma]: That's just one of the many great courses on this aptly named site.

